\c 93 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 93\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Guddina Waaqayyo Mootichaa
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyo mootii dha, inni surraa uffate, aangoos uffatee akka hidhannaattis isa hidhate; biyyi lafaa jabaatee in dhaabata, iddoo isaatiis hin butatu.
\m \bd 2\bd* Teessoon kee durii durii jalqabee jabaatee in dhaabata; ati bara durii durii jalqabdee jirta.
\m \bd 3\bd* Bishaanonni yaa'an ol ka'aniiru, yaa Waaqayyo, bishaanonni yaa'an huursaa isaanii ol kaasaniiru, bishaanonni yaa'an bubbisuu isaanii ol kaasaniiru.
\m \bd 4\bd* Huursaa bishaan baay'ee surraa qabu caalaa, dha'aa galaanaa isa humnaan wal rukutu caalaas, Waaqayyo inni hundumaa gararraa jiru surra-qabeessa!
\m \bd 5\bd* Abboommiin siif dhugaa ba'u, guddaa amanamaa dha, manni kee guyyaa hundumaa qulqullummaatti eegamuun in ta'a, yaa Waaqayyo!
\b 
